HEADWORD: Reng
<hw>Reng</hw> <pr>(r?ng)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See <er>Rank</er>,
<pos>n.</pos>]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A rank; a row.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧In two <xex>renges</xex> fair.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A rung or round of a ladder.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Chaucer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Renidification</ent>⟦br⟧
